OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly dry start but outbreaks
OL,6,Fof rain soon spreading in from the
OL,7,Fwest, turning heavy at times. Becoming
OL,8,Fa little brighter during the afternoon
OL,9,Fwith a few sunny intervals but further
OL,10,Fheavy showers are expected.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRemaining mostly cloudy this
OL,13,Fevening and tonight with frequent
OL,14,Fshowers, some heavy, and a few drier
OL,15,Fclearer intervals. Mainly light winds,
OL,16,Fbut quite breezy along the Solway
OL,17,FCoast.
OL,18,
OL,19,CThursday:FRather cloudy with rain or
OL,20,Fshowers, some turning heavy at times.
OL,21,FWinds will be mainly light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
